      <h1 class='title'>Listed Buildings (Solar Panels)</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c271WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_271ws' title='Col. 271WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c271WS' name='column_271ws' href='#column_271ws' rel='bookmark'>271WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06348'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_326'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-norman-baker' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_326' title='Link to this speech by Mr Norman Baker' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-norman-baker" title="Mr Norman Baker">Norman Baker</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06348">To ask the Deputy Prime Minister what advice he provides to planning authorities on applications to install solar panels on listed buildings. [89074]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06349'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_327'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-tony-mcnulty' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_327' title='Link to this speech by Mr Tony McNulty' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-tony-mcnulty" title="Mr Tony McNulty">Mr. McNulty</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06349">General advice to local authorities about listed building controls is contained in PPG15, Planning and the Historic Environment. Specific advice about solar panels on listed buildings is provided in the new Annex to PPG22 Renewable Energy&#x2014;Annex on Photovoltaics.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
